N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 16 ยง 665.10 - Long distance network services revenues

State Regulations

Long distance network services revenues shall include
revenues derived from the provision of services beyond the basic service area, whether message or flat-rate and including public network switching as well as
private. Notes
